disputes and their consequent instability and refugee problems now
a known bane," he added.
</P>
<P>
"The establishment of an African mechanism for managing and
solving inter-African conflicts is a great development within the
African action framework," the Egyptian minister said.
</P>
<P>
However, he noted that the ability of conflict-management of
African countries have been greatly sapped by their financial
predicament.
</P>
<P>
