<P>
On the Paris bourse, the CAC-40 index finished the session up
45.82 points or 1.13 percent at 4,086.98 after the Pentecost
holiday.
</P>
<P>
The market was boosted by strength in the dollar and a big rise
in index heavyweight France Telecom which closed up nearly 6
percent.
