<HEADLINE> Malaysia to Continue Supporting Efforts to Lift </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, June 3 (Xinhua) -- Malaysia would continue to
support efforts by the United Nations and the Organization of
Islamic Conference (OIC) to lift the seven-year-old economic
sanctions on Iraq, Deputy Foreign Minister Leo Michael Toyad said
Wednesday.
</P>
