</P>
<P>
-- About 30-43 percent of the short and medium-haul flights of
Air France are expected to take off on Wednesday, while only 17
percent of its long-haul flights will be maintained. Talks between
the striking pilots and the management of Air France resumed on
Tuesday afternoon but failed to lead to any agreement so far.
</P>
<P>
-- A few days after the end of its nuclear tests, Pakistan
relaunched the arms race with India by pursuing an intensified
program on ballistic missiles. India announced a 14 percent
increase of its defense budget. 
</P>
