index to 15,554.45 from Monday's nearly 350-point loss, as they
believe the index's top limit lies around 15,530, said an analyst
at a brokerage house.
</P>
<P>
Of the 1,336 issues listed on the First Section, losers
outpaced gainers 771 to 308, with 176 issues remaining unchanged.
</P>
