foreign-funded enterprises in the zone to top 400, and they have
come from 30 countries and regions and brought in a total
investment of one billion U.S. dollars from overseas. Among the 12
transnational corporations that have settled in the zone included
the Microsoft and IBM of the United States and Toshiba of Japan.
