<HEADLINE> Albania May Reconsider Its Kosovo Position: PM </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIRANA, June 3 (Xinhua) -- Albania may have to reconsider its
stand towards the Kosovo issue if the clashes there continue to
escalate, Prime Minister Fatos Nano said Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
Since there is no indication that the Yugoslav government will
abandon its "violent means," Albania would reconsider its attitude
towards the parties involved in the clashes, said Nano at a
regular government meeting.
