<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, June 2 (Xinhua) -- Marco Pantani finished second in
Tuesday's 17th stage of the Tour of Italy and snatched the pink
jersey of overall leader.
</P>
<P>
Pantani placed second to fellow Italian Giuseppe Guerini at the
finish line in Selva Di Val Gardena, taking the leading position
for the first time in his career.
</P>
